      • chain

        public static AnnotationInspector chain(AnnotationInspector first,
                                        AnnotationInspector second)
        Chains two annotation inspectors. The second inspector is only called should the first not find the annotation.
        Parameters:
        first - the first annotation inspector to call.
        second - the second annotation inspector to call, should the first return null.
        Returns:
        the annotation, as found by either the first or the second inspectors.
